lctools(1) -- tools for controlling clouds
==========================================

## DESCRIPTION

**lctools** is a set of tools for controlling
clouds -- list, create and drop nodes, list
images (also known as templates for some providers),
possible node sizes etc.

**lctools** uses **libcloud** for all cloud operations
so actually should support all the providers 
that **libcloud** itself supports.

## FILES

 * `~/.lcrc`:
   Main configuration file, see lcrc(5) for details

